256
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:49,080
Vítej doma, Ai-chan!

257
00:18:48,380 --> 00:18:49,840
Gratulujeme!

258
00:18:50,340 --> 00:18:52,460
Všichni, jsem doma!

259
00:18:52,460 --> 00:18:54,460
Pojďme, mistře.

260
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:55,990
Dobrá...

